# meraki_networks_wireless_ssids_eap_override (Resource)



## Example Usage

```terraform

  eapol_key = {

    retries       = 5
    timeout_in_ms = 5000
  }
  identity = {

    retries = 5
    timeout = 5
  }
  max_retries = 5
  network_id  = "string"
  number      = "string"
  timeout     = 5
}
```
